    <span>📌 total <span class="stat-value" id="stat-total">0</span></span>
    <span>⚡ action req. <span class="stat-value" id="stat-action">0</span></span>
    <span>👤 unique owners <span class="stat-value" id="stat-owners">0</span></span>
